    "Special tokens, like a class token, are also added to grasp the overall meaning of the entire sequence.",
    "The concept of tokenization and special tokens is illustrated in Fig. 1.",
    "Dataset configurationsWe employ three datasets, namely DAVIS, Binding DB, and BIOSNAP, to train and evaluate the DLM-DTI.",
